                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-59-off311 t17930410-59-cd312"></join>, a pair of cotton stockings, value 4 s. a pair of worsted stockings, value 2 s. and two worsted stockings, value 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930410-59-victim569" type="victimName">
                     Albert 
                     Creaton
                  <interp inst="t17930410-59-victim569" type="surname" value="Creaton"></interp>
