            .</p>
               <p>Indicted in a SECOND COUNT laying it to be the property of 
               <persName id="t17930410-59-victim570" type="victimName">
                  Elizabeth, the <rs id="t17930410-59-viclabel313" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-59-victim570 t17930410-59-viclabel313"></join>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-59-person571 t17930410-59-viclabel313"></join> of the said 
